{"tid":476941,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解會無女？","createTime":"2017-11-22T13:06:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-23T00:04:37.000Z","uid":103799,"like":40,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"2bd97f81824338af9932df1c7412c033b4cb83f8","tid":476941,"uid":103799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T13:06:12.000Z","msg":"其實無女，會唔會係自己眼角太高，而唔係女人眼角太高。<br />\n<br />\n個個都要搵個靚女，女神。咁人地咁好條件，就緊係搵門當戶對既有錢靚仔帶財華人士。<br />\n<br />\n細心諗下自己咩條件，<br />\n如果自己樣衰既，就搵返個樣衰既女。<br />\n<br />\n自己窮，就搵返個窮。<br />\n<br />\n自己毒撚，就搵返個毒女。<br />\n<br />\n咁先係門當戶對，係要迫自己得到女神，何苦呢"},{"pid":"916aca38ee5bac82aabd4f1f08c8a6baf488af76","tid":476941,"uid":20867,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T13:10:37.000Z","msg":"有人寧缺勿濫 有人寧濫勿缺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"683cc80324be93715168bb8d7c2cbcd5af00d011","tid":476941,"uid":124899,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T13:25:33.000Z","msg":"唔靚咁要黎做乜，要女都係想扑野舒服。<br />\n<br />\n唔靚，就攞左女人，煩西貪，對自己都無乜好處。<br />\n<br />\n要人傾計，不如要男性朋友好過喇。"},{"pid":"e8dc6ded81e54f3c952542a2ece9f2c77523b53f","tid":476941,"uid":15823,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T13:27:53.000Z","msg":"過到自己過唔到細佬"},{"pid":"7937dd1e36b5c6546c27e83adc7e9bc3ab8a3a2c","tid":476941,"uid":23833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T13:39:07.000Z","msg":"撞墻死啦傻鳩"},{"pid":"4760d90ba319985fc3f5413717b985f1747ce5dd","tid":476941,"uid":103799,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T13:46:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過到自己過唔到細佬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁其實人地靚女都係過唔到自己，要下半成跟住個男人喎<br />\n<br />\n門當戶對跟本唔係上一代產物，而係人人都係咁，你有條件既時候，都要想搵返個條件相襯既"},{"pid":"81bc7eebb4e12884da949b640a362bcfd4aa023c","tid":476941,"uid":103799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T13:46:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>撞墻死啦傻鳩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n溝到女神未呀？"},{"pid":"ffcbdaa39daa221d02b1344b11c9b2ec99dd8e6c","tid":476941,"uid":15823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T13:59:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>過到自己過唔到細佬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁其實人地靚女都係過唔到自己，要下半成跟住個男人喎<br />\n<br />\n門當戶對跟本唔係上一代產物，而係人人都係咁，你有條件既時候，都要想搵返個條件相襯既</blockquote><br />\n所以咪會無女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無料又想要更多咪抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f46d428998f3a0088aeafe8c1a70137a36eb997d","tid":476941,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T14:16:29.000Z","msg":"連樣衰又美極既女都唔揀我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以點"},{"pid":"778b29c6609cf335d4e6ed73ea54b54d8385db05","tid":476941,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T14:19:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連樣衰又美極既女都唔揀我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以點</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"825321b06bda33c57c9f548b51f2aecf0a6e5ba4","tid":476941,"uid":56833,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T14:22:02.000Z","msg":"但好多毒撚比人讚2句 吹捧下就以為自己係中上 係男神 真係睇到我都覺得尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"172a87bb712d409b6f3339d28028ec77f68ed0fb","tid":476941,"uid":21672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T14:27:50.000Z","msg":"有毒撚fd條件唔好<br />\n但成日問邊出到pool<br />\n言談之間又成日話自己又窮又柒<br />\n好無自信又大怨念<br />\n係好難溝到女的"},{"pid":"5e991172836777704aea1e2d90ac59d5ed80afe1","tid":476941,"uid":135986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T14:40:09.000Z","msg":"都係想走肥姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <strong></strong><br />\n唔係想無女"},{"pid":"abe9bde0d170508a501fa41ece140eed08ee055b","tid":476941,"uid":57186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0